#!/usr/bin/env bash
set -euo pipefail

cat >&2 <<'EOF'
error: observer-loop has been removed.

Pizor now forbids polling/sleep-based lifecycle monitoring. Worker lifecycle
updates must be delivered by node-to-node messages. Workers submit sidecar
reports with .pi/scripts/worker-report-submit, which updates the registry and
sends a WORKER_REPORT_POINTER to the current master and observer panes.
EOF
exit 2
